### ===================================================================
### Panopticon Connector — Extensions
### ===================================================================

### List installed extensions (Panopticon)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/extensions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### List installed extensions, with filters
# Filters:
# - filter[search]  string  Search by extension name
# - filter[type]    string  Extension type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/extensions?filter[type]=component
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Get extension details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/extensions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Install extension from URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/extensions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"url": "https://example.com/extension.zip"
}

### ===================================================================
### Panopticon Connector — Core Update
### ===================================================================

### Get core update status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/core/update
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Change update source
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/core/update/source
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"source": "https://update.joomla.org/core/list.xml"
}

### Download core update package
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/core/update/download
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Download core update package (chunked)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/core/update/download/chunked
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"offset": 0,
	"length": 1048576
}

### Activate downloaded update
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/core/update/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Disable core update
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/core/update/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Run post-update tasks
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/core/update/postupdate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Prepare checksum verification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/core/update/checksum/prepare
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Execute checksum verification step
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/core/update/checksum/step
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### ===================================================================
### Panopticon Connector — Akeeba Backup
### ===================================================================

### Get Akeeba Backup info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/akeebabackup/info
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### ===================================================================
### Panopticon Connector — Admin Tools
### ===================================================================

### Unblock IP address
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"ip": "192.168.1.100"
}

### Disable Admin Tools system plugin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/plugin/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Enable Admin Tools system plugin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/plugin/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Disable .htaccess protection
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/htaccess/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Enable .htaccess protection
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/htaccess/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Create temporary super user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/tempsuperuser
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"expiration": 3600
}

### Start security scan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/scanner/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Execute security scan step
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/scanner/step
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### List security scan results
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/scans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Read specific security scan
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/scans/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Read scan alert
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/admintools/scans/1/alerts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### ===================================================================
### Panopticon Connector — Update Sites
### ===================================================================

### List update sites
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/updatesites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Get update site details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/updatesites/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Update an update site
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/updatesites/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"enabled": 1
}

### Delete an update site
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/updatesites/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Rebuild update sites table
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/updatesites/rebuild
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### ===================================================================
### Panopticon Connector — Extension Updates
### ===================================================================

### Refresh available extension updates
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/updates/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

### Apply pending extension updates
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/updates/apply
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"eid": "123"
}

### ===================================================================
### Panopticon Connector — Template Overrides
### ===================================================================

### List changed template overrides
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/template/overrides/changed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json

### Read a changed template override
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/index.php/v1/panopticon/template/overrides/changed/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.api+json
